"1/4 cup light mayonnaise","3 tablespoons fat-free sour cream","1 tablespoon lemon juice","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/4 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","2 cups cubed Red Delicious apple (about 1/2 pound)","1 1/2 cups cubed cooked turkey breast","1 cup seedless red grapes, halved","1/2 cup diced celery","2 tablespoons chopped walnuts, toasted","  Lettuce leaves (optional)"